2 Lamb Ribs
Polenta
1 Onion, diced
3 Cloves Garlic, minced
2cm Ginger, minced
2Tbsp Tomato Paste
1Kg Tomatoes
4Tbsp Natural Peanut Butter
1 Cassava, chopped
1/2 Tbsp Dawa Dawa, ground
2 Habaneros, halved
2 Bunches Dandelion
2tsp Turmeric
1tsp Cardamom
1tsp Coriander
Clarified Butter


MISE
Show Dawa Dawa
Show Polenta
Show Peanut Butter
Show Lamb Ribs
Peel Garlic
Peel Ginger
Half Habaneros
Dice Onion
Chop Dandelion
Chop Cassava 
	note: traditionally use matoke in similar recipes, but not available and plantains are too flavorful.
Dice Tomatoes
Grind Dawa Dawa
Grind Garlic Ginger


COOK
saute onions
add garlic
add ginger
add turmeric
Add tomato paste
Add diced tomatoes
Add peanut butter
Add water little by little while stirring
Season with salt
Add sliced plantains or cassava
add dawa dawa
Add habanero
bring to a boil
Add dandelion or collard greens
Boil for 30min

Make Polenta
Add Butter
Sear polenta in clarified butter
Sear lamb chops

PLATE 
	polenta
	sauce
	lamb chops